column2: SELECT a.apogee_id, a.aspcap_id, m.SDSS_ID, s.ra, s.dec, params.*, paramerrs.*, elems.*, elemerrs.*, dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN (a.aspcapflag) , dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN (a.starflag) into mydb.MyTable_# FROM mydb.Dani_table_Chiara as m JOIN aspcapStar AS a on a.apogee_id = m.SDSS_ID CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams (a.aspcap_id) params CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs (a.aspcap_id) paramerrs CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElems (a.aspcap_id) elems CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemErrs (a.aspcap_id) elemerrs WHERE (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag (#) ) = # and a.extratarg = #
